responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B6BF2C7742380D0E10EEE78445F63F94", "Lionhold was the foothold forged by the vanguard of the Kaelar Army. Discipline and diligence will lead you far, but the march to glory always begins with your first steps in Lionhold.")
